class code_General.modelFiles.organizationModel.Organization(*args, **kwargs)¶

Bases: django.db.models.Model

Profile management class for organizations.

SubID:

Unique ID for that person returned by Auth0, primary key

HashedID:

SHA-512 hashed value of the subID for anonymous identification

Name:

Nickname returned by Auth0, used for filter searches in DB

Details:

Address, tax id and so on

Users:

Link to users belonging to that organization

SupportedServices:

Array of service codes that this organization supports

Uri:

Representation link inside the knowledge graph

CreatedWhen:

Automatically assigned date and time(UTC+0) when the entry is created

UpdatedWhen:

Date and time at which the entry was updated

AccessedWhen:

Last date and time the data was fetched from the database, automatically set
